body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting Martin Motors. My name is Harold Martin. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hello Harold, my name is Maria Perez.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Maria. To assist you better, may I kindly ask for your date of birth?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, my date of birth is the twenty-third of September, nineteen ninety-five.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Maria. And can you also provide me with the last four digits of your phone number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course, the last four digits are five six seven eight.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Great, thank you for providing that information. Is there anything else you would like to share regarding your experience with our Car Dealership in relation to privacy?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I was surprised by the amount of personal data your company had on file.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I appreciate you sharing that feedback, Maria. Your privacy is important to us. Thank you for taking the time to discuss this. Do you have any other concerns or questions I can help address?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, that's all for now. Thank you for your assistance, Harold.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: You're welcome, Maria. If you need anything else, feel free to reach out. Thank you for your time. Have a great day!
